{"tid":259371,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"任志剛：若再爆發金融危機 料「可以好厲害」","createTime":"2017-05-26T23:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T10:44:46.000Z","uid":10295,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2e898d27311930ff03949d56e0038f4911ac6fe","tid":259371,"uid":10295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T23:43:26.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】前金管局總裁任志剛表示，過去每十年便發生金融危機，認為若下次再爆發危機，較之前「可以好厲害」 ，因為九七、九八年的金融風暴及O八年金融海嘯的根源問題尚未解決，包括金融文化及金融全球化的問題。<br />\n<br />\n金融文化方面，他指，現時的金融機構依然為求利益以服務自己為主，而非服務實體經濟。金融全球化方面，在全球量寬下，大量游資四處流竄，影響金融安全。他認為有關情況值得關注，相信下次金融危機起源將來自華爾街模式運作的金融體系。(sw)<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/z60TW5zmrEv.3ugKv7NoOA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzIwO2g9MjU2O2lsPXBsYW5l/http://globalfinance.zenfs.com/images/HK_AHTTP_SINGTAO/20170526d032925_original.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fz60TW5zmrEv.3ugKv7NoOA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzIwO2g9MjU2O2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fglobalfinance.zenfs.com%2Fimages%2FHK_AHTTP_SINGTAO%2F20170526d032925_original.jpg&h=72ffc796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e73c29e6c9d524222092b33aeff83e44ad6f533","tid":259371,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T23:48:15.000Z","msg":"阿媽係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c56ce8686dbb9725879efa3e2c2b5bc3cf36769","tid":259371,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:12:09.000Z","msg":"人人08年都話要反思 去槓桿 實體經濟 綠色經濟 <br />\n<br />\n但人是會做輕鬆果樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc98e10da251bfde9db5d0faa8c707ca46fc4b6","tid":259371,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:13:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人人08年都話要反思 去槓桿 實體經濟 綠色經濟 <br />\n<br />\